9: Mom... Dad... Yumu! Don't leave me!
13: Why do I keep having that dream?!
24:
Well, sitting here isn't gonna do me
any good!
32: Let me show you... my power!
41:
What do you think?! Pretty cool,
right?!
44:
Amazing... I wasn't certain at first,
but you really do possess an
astounding power!
46:
Not just any power either—it's the
power to rewrite reality! Why, that
hasn't been seen since the
beginning of time!
49:
Are you saying that this power could
even change the laws of the
universe?
54:
Cool, right? Now I can go on
adventures with you guys to—
65:
But WHY?! You saw what I can do! I
can fight now!
73: Why? Because I don't want you to.
81:
Ugh, what's with him?! He's always
making ME worry, so what gives him
the right to say what I can or can't
do?!
89:
*sigh* I mean, I get where Alk's
coming from...
99: No... This decision is what's not fair.
113:
You've been having nightmares,
haven't you, Nao?
121:
...It's always the same dream. Mom,
Dad, Yumu... Everyone disappears
on me.
123:
I know they're all alive and well, but
when I'm dreaming, it feels so real.
128: Well, duh, 'cause that's what you are.
132:
Huh... I figured you'd just blow me off
and tell me to quit worrying.
135:
Hmph... Look, if you want your
brother to be safe, you shouldn't try
to fight with powers you don't even
fully understand yet.
139:
...Sorry, but I can't just shrug this off
when your safety's on the line.
141: Listen to your brother, just this once.
144:
In exchange, I'll make you a promise.
I'll make sure he always comes back
to you.
147: Ain't no way I'm letting Alk die on me.
151:
Even after hearing that, you still wish
to get stronger.
159:
Yes! I'm tired of sitting around doing
nothing!
169: Aaand that's why I'm taking over!
179: Wait, wait, wait! Taking over WHAT?!
182:
Your little sister here? Well, she's MY
little sister now!
189:
You don't want me getting hurt,
right? Then all I have to do is get
stronger!
191:
Before you know it, I'll be able to kick
even YOUR butt, so watch out.
199: This was your doing, wasn't it?
202:
I do not know what you are talking
about.
206:
Give it up, Alk. If she's anything like
you, there's no talking her down.
211:
I must agree. Besides... She's in good
hands with the Crimson Blades.
218:
Heh... Now you know what the rest of
us go through with you.
227: Next time, I'll be the one to save YOU!
232:
*sigh* I just hope I never NEED
saving...
